  "summary": "Icon Callout Box: light-blue #E6F0F9 box with left-aligned Brand Blue #00529b Nunito Sans 800 ~21px/28px headline, white rounded-square icon badge with stroke on left edge, vertically centered text, no text under badge, on white background."
